        "3959 - وَ قَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"لاَ يَحْتَكِرُ اَلطَّعَامَ إِلاَّ خَاطِئٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3959 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace be upon him and his family, said:\n\"No one hoards food except a sinner.\""
